@nyder
you need to remember these are designed to have a low file size. Total size of ALL 3 seasons is 11GB vs. around 100GB for all 3 of the original source. These are ripped form bluray. The special thing about the mkv x264 container is that you can achieve very similar quality to the originals with a low bitrate. The people who have files that are 1GB per episode usually do not lower the bitrate, they just convert straight to x264. The point is that, although they are not identical to the original, they are very close in terms of video quality and take up 3x less space than the other x264 and 10x less space than original blu-ray source. 

If you can afford the space and want absolutely perfect files than download the blu-ray version. If you want very similar quality in a manageable  size than get these.

